Package view

Class StudentView

java.lang.Object
view.StudentView
All Implemented Interfaces:
CampsViewer, OwnCampsViewer
public class StudentView extends Object implements CampsViewer, OwnCampsViewer
This class implements CampsViewer and OwnCampsViewer interfaces, providing functionality for students to view and search for camps, view camps they are registered for, and manage enquiries related to camps.
